3. Verify the "Background Image Settings" dialog appears with "Browse", layout, and alignment options, and the "Done" button.
4. Select an image, choose "Keep Aspect Ratio", and "Bottom Right". Click "Done".
5. Save the preset, and observe the preview screen updating correctly.
6. Verify the live projector also respects these new layout rules.
